# html2chm

* download from [http://download.csdn.net/detail/aipeli/41313](http://download.csdn.net/detail/aipeli/41313 "html2zip")

* run html2chm.exe

	![html2chm.exe](/docs/image4blog/html2chm.exe.png)

* preare source html files
	* eg:git help files
	* git help files  [dir](_blank "C:/Users/XXXX/AppData/Local/GitHub/XXX/doc/git/html/")	
* create dir info

   ![generate dir info](/docs/image4blog/generate.png)

*  create chm file

  ![compile](/docs/image4blog/compile.png)

        
* show it now:

  ![show-git.chm](/docs/image4blog/show-git.chm.png)

  
